This project shows how a custom actuator endpoints are created

NOTE - Read operation you can try in browser but for write and delete operation testing use POSTMAN..
...............................................................................................
* Read operation URL - GET -  http://localhost:8080/actuator/loadMyName

* Write operation URL - POST - http://localhost:8080/actuator/loadMyName
Request Body
{
    "name" : "John";
}

* Delete operation URL - DELETE - http://localhost:8080/actuator/loadMyName
...............................................................................................
Postman collection - Custom Actuator.postman_collection.json

Only 3 are there as of 06 March 2026 (DeleteOperation, PostOperation, PostOperation)


